config QORVO_CMD170P4
	bool "Qorvo CMD170P4 RF power detector driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_QORVO_CMD170P4_ENABLED
	select ADC
	help
	  Enable driver for the Qorvo CMD170P4 7.5-9 GHz driver amplifier
	  with integrated power detector. The driver uses table-based
	  interpolation to convert detector voltage (0-5V) to RF output
	  power (0-30 dBm) according to the manufacturer's transfer function.
